title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your heart might be bigger than your treasure chest of intellectual resources. However, trying to please a friend or group could lead you astray if you lose track of your priorities now. Theres a distinct difference between helping others out and manipulating peoples emotions. Only you can accurately judge why you went the extra mile to connect. You may end up putting yourself under stress if you attempt to go too far, dissatisfying yourself and others in the process. Sensibly assess what you can do and promise no more than that. Be the reason someone smiles today. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
